{"tid":2262382,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"PK鄧曾做高薪老臨 「影帝」上身拍片撐維穩歌自high過戲癮","createTime":"2020-10-29T05:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T06:54:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"266796e4a86d578c59aeabf8846681f8556b5860","tid":2262382,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:44:05.000Z","msg":"「被警務生涯耽誤演藝事業」，香港警務處處長「PK鄧」鄧炳強曾揚言自己跟成龍學做警察，又喜歡拖馬跟明星足球隊埋堆，更在今年2月香港最嚴峻的疫情下，跟一眾藝人及警員舉行「撐警無罩宴」，又攬頭攬頸唱K，宴上眾人口沫橫飛，如此高調廣結知己的處長，可謂前無古人，後無來者。<br />\n<br />\n講起做戲，PK鄧曾經做過高薪老臨，黃百鳴也踢爆PK鄧，唔止拍新藝城一部戲，難怪間唔中會身痕過戲癮。今日香港警察官方facebook貼出一條宣傳片，硬sell撐警維穩歌《捍衛香港》，該首歌由鍾鎮濤創作，片中以洗腦式翻loop歌10秒，全程只播幾句，而PK鄧亦粉墨登場。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201029/6J75LCJZUVEP5F2U7AAEEOOTO4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201029%2F6J75LCJZUVEP5F2U7AAEEOOTO4%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5Kimg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=bcd37e57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201029%2F6J75LCJZUVEP5F2U7AAEEOOTO4%2F&h=a8c06cb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201029/6J75LCJZUVEP5F2U7AAEEOOTO4/</a>"},{"pid":"ca6fb73be789f894c047281bd9bd3375c67f0a91","tid":2262382,"uid":93649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:47:42.000Z","msg":"錢嘉樂黎既"},{"pid":"7411a2b9115f39f07cfd943e59ebac741bea976e","tid":2262382,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:48:12.000Z","msg":"好落力做PR，睇嚟仲想上位，做局長，司長，甚至特首 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2efb2f38a53f92c213bcf9416db63711d4fbec5","tid":2262382,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"不務正業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7f8d27f62a6bf1ff5302f5f014bb145287cc37","tid":2262382,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB